student.model

Class ProxyUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • student.model.ProxyUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUser, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class ProxyUser
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUser, java.io.Serializable
    Private class to decorate an IUser to override the equals() and hashCode() methods so that a dictionary, e.g. Hashtable, can properly compare IUsers.
    Author:
    swong
    See Also:
